Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 of Hand MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Arthritis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And a multiple selection localizer is enabled
And 'Joint effusion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Synovitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Synovitis with pannus formation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Inflammatory bone marrow edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Erosions' checkbox is enabled
And 'Proliferative bone changes' checkbox is enabled
And 'Chondropathy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Tenosynovitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Bursitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Destructions' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mutilations' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ankylosis' checkbox is enabled

And 'Differential diagnosis' dropdown menu is enabled
